        <entry>
          <string>Description</string>
          <string>Replace delay with system that saves values on the next tick. A register will hold the to save register and value. Then, it will save on that +1 tick to a register, ensuring it arrives before the clock. Selected operands should check if that register is about to be updated, and if so take the new data instead of old.</string>
